    "body": "### Feature already in Vim?\r\n\r\nNot that I know of\r\n\r\n### Feature description\r\n\r\nIn the lua api there is currently the function `nvim_set_hl()` which sets a highlight group, it also overrides the highlight group that you specify if it already exists. The `:highlight` command is able to modify and not override a highlight group. Could there be a lua function that allows you to modify but not override a highlight group?\r\n\r\nI have looked in the open and closed Issues and I can't find anything similar to this.",
